column5: I'm going up to Witch Bay Camp for the first time the middle of next week. If anybody has any fishing reports (walleye, musky, northern, smallmouth), I would love to hear them. Thanks.

Dave, check their website at www.witchbay.comThey regularly post fishing reports. From what I've heard so far, the fishing has been fantastic, much better than last year which was unbelieveable even then. And although this may sound like one of those "you should have been here last week" stories, the fishing never dropped off last year, at least for walleyes.
